Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:44.13,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3c&HD75400&}会いにいこう！
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.93,0:16:30.56,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3c&H00B0B7&}我这就带你过去！
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.01,0:16:39.56,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3c&H00B0B7&}山上有非常美妙的东西
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.04,0:16:43.49,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3c&H00B0B7&}究竟会有什么呢？
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.87,0:16:49.29,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3c&H00B0B7&}到了之后你就知道啦
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.88,0:16:54.71,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3c&H00B0B7&}真想快点让你看到！
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.43,0:17:00.17,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3c&H00B0B7&}我能听到歌声
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.17,0:17:03.39,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3c&H00B0B7&}在呼唤我向这边走
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.39,0:17:06.56,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3c&H00B0B7&}仿佛在向我招手一般
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.56,0:17:10.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3c&H00B0B7&}树叶被风轻轻吹动
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.97,0:17:14.36,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3c&H107AF1&}小溪潺潺而流
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.36,0:17:17.89,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3c&H107AF1&}鸟儿婉转歌唱
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.89,0:17:21.21,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3c&H107AF1&}都在呼唤着我
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.21,0:17:25.53,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3c&H107AF1&}快点登上山顶吧
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.53,0:17:28.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3c&HD75400&}要是累得走不动了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.15,0:17:32.28,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3c&HD75400&}那就手牵着手
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.28,0:17:35.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3c&HD75400&}一起爬上去吧
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.79,0:17:40.01,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3c&HD75400&}美妙的东西在等着我们！
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.01,0:17:41.95,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3c&HD75400&}再等等！ 再等等！
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.95,0:17:44.13,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3c&HD75400&}马上就来看你！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:23.32,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&HEF598C&\fax-0.1}手が届きそうな　星のあかりが流れてく、空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.32,0:18:43.37,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&HEF598C&\fax-0.1}それはまるでレールのように私たちの想いを運んでくれているみたいね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.23,0:18:59.12,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&HEF598C&\fax-0.1}小さなまたたき……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.40,0:19:41.81,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&H15E400&\fax-0.1}願い事は誰も見えないくらい　ほのかに輝いているんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.39,0:19:56.52,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&H15E400&\fax-0.1}蛍が光を慈しむように抱きしめ舞いながら飛ぶのはね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:20:13.96,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&H15E400&\fax-0.1}ここにいるよって、あの空の星へと伝えるためだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:27.47,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&H15E400&\fax-0.1}叶えたい夢を……きっと
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.20,0:18:23.32,IN-CH,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&HEF598C&\fax-0.1}仿佛触手可及 星光划过天空
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.32,0:18:43.37,IN-CH,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&HEF598C&\fax-0.1}光芒如铁道一般 带走我们的思绪
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.23,0:18:59.12,IN-CH,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&HEF598C&\fax-0.1}微弱的星光闪烁……
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.40,0:19:41.81,IN-CH,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&H15E400&\fax-0.1}愿望散发出微弱的光芒 仿佛无人能看到
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.39,0:19:56.52,IN-CH,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&H15E400&\fax-0.1}萤火虫之所以将那微光 拥抱在怀中飞舞
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.09,0:20:13.96,IN-CH,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&H15E400&\fax-0.1}是为了告诉满天的繁星 它就在这里
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.15,0:20:27.47,IN-CH,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fad(300,300)\blur3\3c&H15E400&\fax-0.1}一定要实现这份梦想
Comment: 0,0:20:41.64,0:20:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,ED “Believe like Singing.”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.64,0:20:51.98,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}誰だっておなじように　心を持っているんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:21:02.87,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}本当は感じられるんだよ、あなたのその痛みだって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:12.04,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}重なった手と手のぬくもり知ってるから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.88,0:21:22.68,OP-JP,,50,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}自分だってできる何かを探して
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:24.76,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}We believe like Singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.76,0:21:30.23,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}たった一つ、ほんの少し　きっかけを抱きしめるの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.23,0:21:35.69,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}きっといつか　ずっと側で　そう願う優しさを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:41.28,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}大切な声が聴こえる　忘れないで
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.40,0:21:41.95,OP-JP,,0,0,60,,{\fad(300,300)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}Please remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:47.75,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}たった一度、願ってほしい　奇跡を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.75,0:21:53.25,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}So we always sing a song of wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.42,0:21:58.51,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}見つめ合う様な Heart and Heart.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.64,0:20:51.98,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}原来谁都一样 会有自己的心
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.52,0:21:02.87,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}其实我也能感受到 你的那份伤痛
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.87,0:21:12.04,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}因为知道牵起的手之间的温暖
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.88,0:21:22.68,OP-CH,,50,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}我才会去寻找自己也力所能及的事
Comment: 1,0:21:22.68,0:21:24.76,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}Believe like Singing.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.76,0:21:30.23,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}将那份唯一 又不起眼的契机 收藏在心中
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.23,0:21:35.69,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}你温柔祈愿 愿终有一天 能永伴身边
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.69,0:21:41.28,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}耳边回荡着珍重的话语 「请不要忘记」
Comment: 2,0:21:39.40,0:21:41.95,OP-CH,,0,0,60,,{\fad(300,300)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}Please remember
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.28,0:21:47.75,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}一次就好 希望你能许愿 愿奇迹降临
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.75,0:21:53.25,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}我们总是唱着希望之歌
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.42,0:21:58.51,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}彼此之间 心心相印
